"title": "5272: craftsmen",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5272: craftsmen",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Skilled workers and artisans. God is sometimes compared to a master craftsman in his work of creation. Scripture also identifies God as the giver of talent and ability to certain individuals, in particular those employed in the construction of the tabernacle and the temple.</p>\n<h2>God the Creator seen as a master craftsman</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:19-Prov3:20\">PRO 3:19–3:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:1-Gen1:31\">GEN 1:1–1:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:4-Job38:38\">JOB 38:4–38:38</a> <em>inanimate creation</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:39-Job39:30\">JOB 38:39–39:30</a> <em>animate creation</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:22-Prov8:31\">PRO 8:22–8:31</a></p>\n<h2>Craftsmen employed in the construction of the tabernacle and its furnishings</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod31:1-Exod31:11\">EXO 31:1–31:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod26:1\">EXO 26:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod26:31\">EXO 26:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:6-Exod28:8\">EXO 28:6–28:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:15\">EXO 28:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:30-Exod36:3\">EXO 35:30–36:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod36:8-Exod38:11\">EXO 36:8–38:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:1-Exod39:3\">EXO 39:1–39:3</a></p>\n<h2>Craftsmen employed in the construction of the temple and its furnishings</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:13-1Kgs7:45\">1KI 7:13–7:45</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr4:2-2Chr4:6\">2CH 4:2–4:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr4:10-2Chr4:16\">2CH 4:10–4:16</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs5:17-1Kgs5:18\">1KI 5:17–5:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr22:14-1Chr22:16\">1CH 22:14–22:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:3-1Chr29:5\">1CH 29:3–29:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:5-2Chr2:7\">2CH 2:5–2:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:13-2Chr2:14\">2CH 2:13–2:14</a></p>\n<h2>Craftsmen employed in the manufacture of idols</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:19-Isa40:20\">ISA 40:19–40:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:5-Isa41:7\">ISA 41:5–41:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:9-Isa44:20\">ISA 44:9–44:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:3-Jer10:10\">JER 10:3–10:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos8:4-Hos8:6\">HOS 8:4–8:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos13:2\">HOS 13:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:23-Acts19:41\">ACT 19:23–19:41</a></p>\n<h2>Carpenters</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam5:11\">2SA 5:11</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr14:1\">1CH 14:1</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:12\">2CH 24:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:13\">ISA 44:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:9\">EZK 27:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:55\">MAT 13:55</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:3\">MRK 6:3</a></p>\n<h2>Gem cutters</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:11\">EXO 28:11</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Masons</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:12\">2CH 24:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr22:14-1Chr22:16\">1CH 22:14–22:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra3:7\">EZR 3:7</a></p>\n<h2>Goldsmiths</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa46:6\">ISA 46:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh3:31-Neh3:32\">NEH 3:31–3:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:17\">JER 51:17</a></p>\n<h2>Silversmiths</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:4\">PRO 25:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg17:4\">JDG 17:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:24\">ACT 19:24</a></p>\n<h2>Potters</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:21\">ROM 9:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr4:23\">1CH 4:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa64:8\">ISA 64:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer18:2-Jer18:4\">JER 18:2–18:4</a></p>\n<h2>Weavers and embroiderers</h2>\n<h3>Skilled craftsmen</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:35\">EXO 35:35</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod26:1\">EXO 26:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod26:31\">EXO 26:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:6\">EXO 28:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:15\">EXO 28:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:22\">EXO 39:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:27\">EXO 39:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:9-Isa19:10\">ISA 19:9–19:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa38:12\">ISA 38:12</a></p>\n<h3>A weaver's shuttle</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job7:6\">JOB 7:6</a></strong></p>\n<h3>A weaver's rod</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr20:5\">1CH 20:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:7\">1SA 17:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam21:19\">2SA 21:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr11:23\">1CH 11:23</a></p>\n<h2>Craftsmen taken into exile</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs24:10-2Kgs24:17\">2KI 24:10–24:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa3:1-Isa3:3\">ISA 3:1–3:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer24:1\">JER 24:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:2\">JER 29:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer52:12-Jer52:16\">JER 52:12–52:16</a></p>\n<h2>Craftsmen in place-names</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr4:14\">1CH 4:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh11:31-Neh11:35\">NEH 11:31–11:35</a></p>\n<h2>Metaphorical references to craftsmen</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:22-Prov8:31\">PRO 8:22–8:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:25\">ISA 41:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa64:8\">ISA 64:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer18:6\">JER 18:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech1:20-Zech1:21\">ZEC 1:20–1:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:10\">1CO 3:10</a></p>",
